---js
{
  "title":"Videos",
  "description": "Lists any public videos for presentations, product demos, or events where I've presented.",  
  "layout": "generic",
  "pagination": {
    "data": "videos",
    "size": 20,
    "alias": "items",
    "reverse": true,
    "before": function(data, fullData) { 
      return Array.from(data).sort((a, b) => {
        return a.date > b.date ? 1 : -1;
      });
    }
  },
  "headerImage": "/images/headers/header-videos.jpg",
  "headerImageAltText": "A cropped image of a Video editing application on a laptop",
  "headerImageAttribution": "Photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@mattykwong1?utm_content=creditCopyText&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=unsplash\">Matthew Kwong</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/person-using-macbook-pro-turned-on-qJgW5ewKCO8?utm_content=creditCopyText&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=unsplash\">Unsplash</a>"
}
---

<p>Often when I present at a conference, the event records the presentation and makes them available online. Sometimes I fo a webinar or a product demonstration and the recording is made available. This page lists any public videos for presentations, product demos, or events where I've presented.</p>

{% include 'pagination-count.html' %}

<ul class="posts">
  {% for item in items %}
    <li>
      <h4>
        {{ item.title }}
      </h4>
      <span class="date">
        <strong>Date:
        </strong>
        {{ item.date }}
        {% if item.url.length > 0 %}
          |
          <a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank">
            <strong>Link to Video</strong>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      </span>
      {% if item.description %}
        {{ item.description }}
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

